Class IMatchesRank

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.IMatchesRank
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<IMatchesRank>

    public class IMatchesRank
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<IMatchesRank>
    Represents a sub-set of the results of an instance-matching query executed via an IStore object, all of which have been assigned an identical ranking-value by the matching mechanism.
